1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:16,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:27,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:33,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:42,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:51,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:01:02,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:17,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:02,980
[Episode 8]

23
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:10,410
All the poisons have already been destroyed.

24
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:13,540
Why then does the Begonia Pendant still react so strangely?

25
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:17,410
Could it be that there are still other toxins hidden within the palace?

26
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,660
Princess Ying's mind is unclear.

27
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,980
Her words cannot be taken as truth.

28
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,540
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:35,930
Your Highness,

30
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:37,770
I mean no disrespect.

31
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:39,290
It is by His Majesty's command.

32
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:42,100
Should a single lamp be lit in this cold palace,

33
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,130
a guard's life must be taken in exchange.

34
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,610
I'm truly fearful.

35
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,780
Ying.

36
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,410
Ying.

37
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,540
Ying.

38
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:30,340
Ying.

39
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,660
I'm your brother.

40
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,730
I have come to see you.

41
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:39,260
Qianqing!

42
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,500
Come.

43
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,610
Ying.

44
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,410
It's so cold,

45
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:58,260
remember to keep your shoes on from now on.

46
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:09,820
Ying.

47
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,290
Stop painting.

48
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,940
Your brother and I have come to see you.

49
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,220
Ying.

50
00:04:18,910 --> 00:04:21,260
I brought you osmanthus and red bean dumplings.

51
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,260
After you eat them,

52
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,690
you should go to sleep early.

53
00:04:29,030 --> 00:04:31,290
How did you know I like these?

54
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:40,060
Who are you?

55
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,140
Then do you want to eat them?

56
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:50,250
When I've killed them all,

57
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,730
then I'll eat.

58
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,340
Kill whom?

59
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,220
Why don't you help me,

60
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,410
and kill them all?

61
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,850
Mother, this teacup is exquisite.

62
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,540
Fine porcelain,

63
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:46,730
so clear and delicate.

64
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:50,140
Ying's illness

65
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,730
has always come and gone.

66
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,170
After much effort to nurse her,

67
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:56,460
her confusion still outweighs her clarity.

68
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,490
That Xiao Huan

69
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,250
is determined to take our lives!

70
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:03,850
Mother.

71
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,900
Ying gave poison to the Empress,

72
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,020
and attempted to assassinate His Majesty.

73
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:10,580
She was only punished by ten days without lighting a lamp.

74
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,610
That punishment is already merciful enough.

75
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,610
Ying has never been of sound mind.

76
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,340
But why did she become this way?

77
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,610
You know the reason well.

78
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:22,460
Had it not been for that great fire at Luling Palace back then,

79
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,100
when Xiao Huan abandoned her,

80
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:26,540
she would never have been so deeply scarred.

81
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,580
Then

82
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,780
why did Luling Palace suddenly burn for no reason?

83
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,980
What do you mean by that?

84
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:35,490
You are my own flesh and blood,

85
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:37,130
the child I carried for ten months,

86
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:39,140
born through hardship and pain.

87
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,700
Do you not know why,

88
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,100
or for whom, I have done all this?

89
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:51,730
So Mother has always known

90
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,170
the truth behind Ying's madness,

91
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,020
yet chose never to tell her,

92
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,900
encouraging her instead to resent His Majesty.

93
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,140
Is this, Mother,

94
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:01,460
what you call love for me and Ying?

95
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,660
So,

96
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,660
it is because of your sister's matter

97
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,020
that you have borne a grudge against me all this time.

98
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,660
You were in Southern Chu for so many years,

99
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:24,410
yet not once did you send a letter home.

100
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:27,140
Whatever I asked you to do,

101
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,610
you brushed aside carelessly,

102
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,540
and even

103
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,580
stood against me.

104
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,140
Mother.

105
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,050
You speak too harshly.

106
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,610
Does it hurt?

107
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,340
It does not.

108
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,020
Mother,

109
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,140
please be at ease.

110
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,250
Now that I have returned,

111
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,410
I shall protect you and my sister with all that I am.

112
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,410
I will never let either of you suffer again.

113
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,580
The injustice Ying endured,

114
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,540
I will never forget.

115
00:08:56,950 --> 00:08:57,580
Well?

116
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,610
Did you meet His Majesty?

117
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,460
Does that mean I can stop practicing?

118
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,300
Look at me,

119
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:03,820
do I look like I've met him?

120
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,460
Then what should we do?

121
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:11,300
His Majesty could summon Song Lanxi at any moment.

122
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,610
He values him so highly.

123
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,960
Even if I practice until I'm perfect,

124
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,850
the moment His Majesty sees the real one, I'll be exposed.

125
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,180
His Majesty

126
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:19,980
is gravely ill now.

127
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,820
He is unlikely to grant an audience for the time being.

128
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,700
As for you,

129
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,010
put your mind to practicing your calligraphy first.

130
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,220
We'll talk once you've fooled the officials in the Capital.

131
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,370
Come,

132
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:30,490
show me.

133
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,770
Your writing

134
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,460
does resemble his,

135
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,130
yet it still lacks spirit.

136
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,370
Anyone who has seen Song Lanxi's true work

137
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,820
will see through it at a glance.

138
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,490
Song Lanxi

139
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,580
is a master of calligraphy.

140
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,490
A four chi scroll of his sells for more than a hundred liang of silver.

141
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:55,340
How could that be copied so easily?

142
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,420
At the start, you insisted

143
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,370
on accompanying me to the Capital.

144
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:02,530
You boasted

145
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,420
as if nothing were beyond your ability.

146
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,180
I said I wished to go to the Capital with you,

147
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,650
but did I say I meant to impersonate Song Lanxi?

148
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,300
If you think my writing is poor,

149
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,180
do it yourself if you can.

150
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,650
This robe of mine

151
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,300
is

152
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,490
suited to the Dragon Boat Festival season.

153
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,300
It is costly and difficult to make, you...

154
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:24,820
What now?

155
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:35,010
- What are you doing? - Do not move.

156
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,220
[Turtle]

157
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,890
Do not be angry, Your Highness.

158
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,770
Please look.

159
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:46,460
This is the character I have practiced for over a month,

160
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,580
the one that most resembles his writing.

161
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:48,870
[Turtle]

162
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:49,340
Here.

163
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:54,500
[Turtle]

164
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:57,580
[Turtle]

165
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,850
Characters like this,

166
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,980
how many can you write?

167
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,700
I can write

168
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,180
not many.

169
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,370
About two hundred or so...

170
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,370
Two hundred or so?

171
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:15,820
Come,

172
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,130
write them all for me.

173
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:19,300
Quickly.

174
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:19,980
Sit.

175
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,130
Come,

176
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:22,250
write.

177
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:31,460
Your Highness, you're blocking the light.

178
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,180
I can't have anyone standing here when I'm writing.

179
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,580
Fine.

180
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,300
Hurry and write.

181
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,650
For the Grand Tutor's kindness to me,

182
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:02,980
I would give my body and soul,

183
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,100
and repay it fully.

184
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,490
At the palace examination,

185
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,250
I will

186
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,420
take first place.

187
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,060
Good.

188
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,130
You may go.

189
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,340
Well?

190
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:21,300
Any word of Cangcang?

191
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,060
She claimed she was going to the Summer Palace,

192
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,420
but went to the Sword Cottage instead.

193
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,300
It seems

194
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,180
her visit to the Sword Cottage isn't simple.

195
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,770
Then Father means...

196
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,650
Regarding Li Lu's death,

197
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:45,340
she has never let it go.

198
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,820
How is the truth

199
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:53,690
she seeks coming along?

200
00:13:33,170 --> 00:13:33,990
Master.

201
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,430
I miss you.

202
00:13:38,030 --> 00:13:39,580
The longer I stay in the palace,

203
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:43,300
the more I miss the carefree days I had here.

204
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,490
But you're gone.

205
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:49,940
Xiao Huan won't even give me a reason.

206
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:52,700
Master,

207
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,420
what exactly were you all hiding from me?

208
00:13:58,270 --> 00:13:59,420
The imperial family is heartless,

209
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:01,010
yet Xiao Huan keeps helping me.

210
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:03,060
Why is that?

211
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,490
Why did you kill my master?

212
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,610
I promised him

213
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:11,700
I wouldn't tell you.

214
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,610
What did you say?

215
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,250
What aren't you allowed to tell me?

216
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:32,460
What are you all hiding from me?

217
00:14:51,150 --> 00:14:52,490
You're back, little glutton.

218
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:55,340
What do you want to eat?

219
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:56,770
I will make it for you.

220
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,580
Master, is it ready?

221
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,340
What gift are you giving me?

222
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,300
You may open your eyes now.

223
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,890
What a beautiful pendant.

224
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:21,250
This is a protector I give you.

225
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:23,250
You must keep it with you from now on.

226
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,220
Well?

227
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,100
Do you like it?

228
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,130
I do.

229
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:28,850
Father never remembers my birthday.

230
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:31,100
Master is much better than Father.

231
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,180
Thank you, Master.

232
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,490
I really like it.

233
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,890
As long as you like it.

234
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,820
Master,

235
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,730
can you tell me

236
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:49,100
why Xiao Huan

237
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:52,580
had to kill you?

238
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,300
Who?

239
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,650
Luo.

240
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,010
Cangcang.

241
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,490
Speak.

242
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,250
Why are you here?

243
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,100
I came to pay my respects too,

244
00:16:20,790 --> 00:16:21,770
to share a drink with him.

245
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:31,580
But Master never drank Bamboo Leaf Green.

246
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,370
Are you really here to pay respects?

247
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:49,700
Cangcang,

248
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,370
Father

249
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:53,980
was worried about you.

250
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,370
Luo,

251
00:17:04,390 --> 00:17:06,420
do you still remember this pendant?

252
00:17:07,150 --> 00:17:08,700
This Begonia Pendant

253
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,770
was given to me by Master.

254
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:16,250
He said it would keep me safe.

255
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,730
I remember.

256
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,490
I only learned recently

257
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:33,300
that it is a treasure beyond price.

258
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,050
With it on me,

259
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:38,990
no poison can get close.

260
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:44,010
Master was protecting me all along.

261
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:52,140
But I do not even know why he died.

262
00:17:58,670 --> 00:18:00,930
I do not even know why he died!

263
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,780
Am I that useless?

264
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:13,730
Cang...

265
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:26,060
Cangcang.

266
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:36,900
I remember when I was little,

267
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,780
I loved leaning against this forge.

268
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:43,380
No matter how cold it was outside,

269
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:45,860
it was always warm here.

270
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:23,820
Tell me,

271
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:28,250
when have you ever approached me

272
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,380
without a purpose?

273
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:35,340
No, My Lady.

274
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:36,930
It was Father...

275
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:39,250
Master forged the Rex Sword for you

276
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:43,930
and you used that very sword to kill him.

277
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:47,780
- How am I supposed to trust you again? - I...

278
00:19:50,990 --> 00:19:53,780
How am I supposed to grow old at your side,

279
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:56,780
to live with you in harmony?

280
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,930
Since I became empress,

281
00:19:58,950 --> 00:20:00,170
I've swallowed every grievance.

282
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:02,140
In the palace,

283
00:20:03,230 --> 00:20:05,780
there hasn't been a single day I didn't try to uncover the truth!

284
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:08,020
♪To roam the world with a sword...♪

285
00:20:08,080 --> 00:20:09,170
Tell me the truth!

286
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,820
