He was once a senior minister in the court.

572
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:59,700
After losing to Ling Xuefeng,

573
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,010
he retired to the countryside.

574
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:04,300
Yet his name remains illustrious among the gentry.

575
00:38:04,470 --> 00:38:07,050
Many upright officials in the court were his students.

576
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:10,220
Song Lanxi was also his student.

577
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:10,930
Indeed.

578
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,700
Your Majesty is truly cunning and strategic.

579
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:15,610
So Song Lanxi

580
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:18,260
was merely a lure to draw out Li Chengtian.

581
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,260
Ling Xuefeng killed his beloved student.

582
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:24,450
What would he feel?

583
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:29,410
Your Majesty intends for me to summon Master Li out of retirement.

584
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:33,700
What do you think?

585
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:42,340
[Take care, Song Lan]

586
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,700
Greetings, Father.

587
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,860
Song Lanxi is not dead.

588
00:38:58,130 --> 00:38:58,940
Impossible.

589
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,640
I personally struck him down.

590
00:39:01,620 --> 00:39:03,100
[Take care, Song Lan]

591
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:05,260
This is Song Lanxi's calligraphy.

592
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:10,570
Since you personally attacked him,

593
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:13,130
there must be hidden circumstances.

594
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:16,300
I will investigate further.

595
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,300
Get up.

596
00:39:19,370 --> 00:39:21,340
All traces of Li Lu's interactions with us

597
00:39:21,340 --> 00:39:22,410
should be cleared away.

598
00:39:23,790 --> 00:39:24,670
Rest assured, Father.

599
00:39:25,470 --> 00:39:26,450
Everything has been properly handled.

600
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:27,880
But...

601
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,160
I know you cannot bear it.

602
00:39:35,030 --> 00:39:37,970
And as a father, neither can I.

603
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:41,860
Yet this is the truth she most wishes to know.

604
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:45,410
It is also what she must face.

605
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:49,130
But Young Lady refuses to believe that Li Lu is the Ghost King,

606
00:39:49,550 --> 00:39:51,090
thinking instead that someone framed him.

607
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,530
Who does she suspect?

608
00:39:52,680 --> 00:39:53,900
She has not mentioned it.

609
00:39:54,430 --> 00:39:56,410
She is heading straight to the palace now.

610
00:40:01,060 --> 00:40:03,620
[Wuying Hall]

611
00:40:04,470 --> 00:40:06,010
Is the Empress's favourite pear blossom honey

612
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,130
all ready?

613
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:09,050
Prepared long ago.

614
00:40:13,470 --> 00:40:14,490
Your Majesty,

615
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:15,970
the Empress has arrived.

616
00:40:24,590 --> 00:40:25,380
Why

617
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:26,930
does Your Majesty look so surprised

618
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,090
to see me?

619
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,530
I just thought

620
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,130
you would be happier to step out

621
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:33,700
of the palace for a while.

622
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,260
Why should I be happy?

623
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:47,130
This is pear blossom honey from this year's harvest.

624
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:48,380
Taste it.

625
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:52,410
You haven't finished speaking.

626
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:53,970
Why would I

627
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:56,050
be happy?

628
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,970
Should I be happy

629
00:41:15,590 --> 00:41:17,280
that my master is the Ghost King?

630
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:20,950
What are you talking about?

631
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:23,820
All along, you've had people following me,

632
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:24,860
never leaving my side.

633
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:26,700
Don't you know what I'm talking about?

634
00:41:27,030 --> 00:41:28,380
I had them follow you

635
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:30,300
to protect you.

636
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,570
Since you admit it,

637
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:33,660
then the items of the Ghost King in the Sword Cottage...

638
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,380
You were the one who placed them?

639
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:37,340
You are suspecting me

640
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,300
of framing your master?

641
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:41,180
No.

642
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:43,860
If I truly wanted to frame your master,

643
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:45,530
why wait until today?

644
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:03,860
Then tell me,

645
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:07,660
why did you kill my master?

646
00:42:07,680 --> 00:42:09,090
I promised your master

647
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,180
I wouldn't reveal the truth to you.

648
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,660
Fine.

649
00:42:16,950 --> 00:42:17,970
I'll find out myself.

650
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:19,410
Cangcang,

651
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,410
have you considered

652
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:23,010
that perhaps the truth

653
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,700
is more than you can bear?

654
00:42:24,990 --> 00:42:26,410
If I didn't know the truth,

655
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:29,180
how could I bear it?

656
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:42,490
Ling Xuefeng,

657
00:42:44,030 --> 00:42:46,340
are you betting that I wouldn't break my vow?

658
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:47,860
Grand Tutor Ling has been kind to me.

659
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:51,660
He helped me avenge my daughter's wrongs.

660
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:54,050
He allowed me

661
00:42:54,630 --> 00:42:55,970
to live again.

662
00:42:56,070 --> 00:42:56,860
For him,

663
00:42:57,240 --> 00:42:58,820
I would face mountains of blades and seas of fire,

664
00:42:58,990 --> 00:43:00,700
even if my soul were to shatter,

665
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:02,090
I would not hesitate.

666
00:43:02,950 --> 00:43:04,220
If I told you

667
00:43:04,630 --> 00:43:06,340
that it was Ling Xuefeng

668
00:43:06,840 --> 00:43:07,970
who abducted your daughter?

669
00:43:10,110 --> 00:43:11,380
All of this

670
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:13,130
was orchestrated by him

671
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:14,740
as a bitter ruse.

672
00:43:16,360 --> 00:43:17,130
Impossible.

673
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:20,340
It's impossible.

674
00:43:22,320 --> 00:43:23,860
Everything I saw

675
00:43:23,990 --> 00:43:25,010
was real.

676
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:27,740
Everything I did

677
00:43:27,950 --> 00:43:29,450
was of my own free will.

678
00:43:30,240 --> 00:43:31,900
I was not used by anyone.

679
00:43:32,990 --> 00:43:34,380
I will never regret it.

680
00:43:35,510 --> 00:43:36,300
Is that so?

681
00:43:37,200 --> 00:43:38,180
Then these words,

682
00:43:38,840 --> 00:43:40,380
would you dare to say them to Cangcang?

683
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:49,410
Do not tell Cangcang the truth.

684
00:43:51,070 --> 00:43:51,860
Understood.

685
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:53,930
A promise from the sovereign

686
00:43:54,680 --> 00:43:55,740
is never broken.

